|dead-url=no
}}</ref>alt屬性有時亦會被誤稱為「alt元素」（alt tag，變相與<code>img</code>元素畫上等號）。<ref name="annevk"/><ref>{{web cite | url=http://www.456bereastreet.com/archive/200511/its_alt_attribute_not_alt_tag | title=It-{’}-s alt attribute, not alt tag | work=456 Berea Street | author=Roger Johansson | date=2005-11-07 | accessdate=2009-07-22}}</ref><ref>{{web cite | url=http://www.autisticcuckoo.net/archive.php?id=2004/07/20/tags-elements-attributes | title=Alt tags | work=The Autistic Cuckoo | date=2004-07-20 | author=Tommy Olsson | accessdate=2009-07-22 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071225050529/http://www.autisticcuckoo.net/archive.php?id=2004%2F07%2F20%2Ftags-elements-attributes | archivedate=2007-12-25 }}</ref>

